 <title>Falando em editoração...</title>
 <link>http://mutgamb.org/blog/Falando-em-editoracao</link>
 <description>&lt;p&gt;Cris Ribas, que ainda est&amp;aacute; se familiarizando com Linux &amp;quot;mas super a fim de aprender&amp;quot; pediu indica&amp;ccedil;&amp;otilde;es de softwares para design de impressos e editora&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o. A lista respondeu apontando possibilidades:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Belis&amp;aacute;rio indicou o &lt;a href=&quot;http://www.scribus.net/&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;Scribus&lt;/a&gt;, Varga um &lt;a href=&quot;http://estudiolivre.org/tiki-index.php?page=Softwares%20de%20Gr%C3%A1fico&amp;amp;bl&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;copilado de links no Est&amp;uacute;dio Livre&lt;/a&gt;, e Felipe Fonseca sugeriu &lt;a href=&quot;http://inkscape.org/&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;Inkscape&lt;/a&gt;, pra ilustra&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o vetorial simples:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;blockquote&gt;
	&lt;p&gt;Tinha tamb&amp;eacute;m um software da pr&amp;oacute;pria Corel, acho que era &lt;a href=&quot;http://www.xara.com/&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;CorelXara&lt;/a&gt;. Mas faz tempo que n&amp;atilde;o tento usar. Gimp e plugins pra Bitmaps etc. Pra diagrama&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o estilo DTP pesad&amp;atilde;o tem o Scribus e o &lt;a href=&quot;http://packages.ubuntu.com/search?keywords=scribus-ng&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;Scribus-ng&lt;/a&gt;. Pra coisas mais leves eu uso bastante o&lt;a href=&quot;http://www.lyx.org/&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt; Lyx&lt;/a&gt;. pra ebooks em epub, uso o &lt;a href=&quot;http://code.google.com/p/sigil/&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;Sigil&lt;/a&gt;. E meus &lt;a href=&quot;http://links.metareciclagem.org/tags.php/grafilab&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;tradicionais caminh&amp;otilde;es de links&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
